{"tid":621434,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"頭皮皮膚病問題","createTime":"2018-04-08T10:05:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T04:48:32.000Z","uid":40845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ec6ce36a261d6d695d45b7d7e0bebadd3301d7aa","tid":621434,"uid":40845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T10:05:42.000Z","msg":"三年前開始個頭皮邊緣位開始會有結焦，跟住會自己甩出黎。<br />\n原先只有頭先有，搞搞下連個鼻翼同耳仔後面都有，睇過皮膚科醫生，話係咩xxx增生，冇傳染性，俾咗啲類固醇同藥丸，但係都斷唔到尾。<br />\n有冇人知點樣先可以斷到尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75c753a146adc28777d05f6e1ce904f35301e051","tid":621434,"uid":113234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T10:19:23.000Z","msg":"點解會結焦<br />\n係咪曬傷燒傷過"},{"pid":"acb230caa2fba390038545f5d453133735ad7f0f","tid":621434,"uid":127885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T11:38:24.000Z","msg":"你呢D叫脂漏性皮膚炎。我都有咁嘅情況，不會斷尾的，時好時壞"},{"pid":"2257108362fafc8815d5d8cfb308f364627312ff","tid":621434,"uid":40845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75c753a146adc28777d05f6e1ce904f35301e051","tid":621434,"uid":113234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T10:19:23.000Z","msg":"點解會結焦<br />\n係咪曬傷燒傷過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T15:59:03.000Z","msg":"其實就係會自己生厚厚地既頭皮，有時會自己甩出黎，有時我會&ldquo;拗&rdquo;出黎，屌，好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"762ee30e5ba60f2f879f200782513a52b2d9e28c","tid":621434,"uid":40845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acb230caa2fba390038545f5d453133735ad7f0f","tid":621434,"uid":127885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T11:38:24.000Z","msg":"你呢D叫脂漏性皮膚炎。我都有咁嘅情況，不會斷尾的，時好時壞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T15:59:44.000Z","msg":"不會斷尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我廿幾歲乍，搞到我唔夠敢出街剪頭<img src=\"/a